snippet.title: Fleet Battle V2
snippet.description:
Google Play: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.smuttlewerk.fleetbattle

App Store:
https://itunes.apple.com/de/app/fleet-battle-battle-series/id904275738?mt=8

Fleet Battle V2! Out now for your mobile device! 

- Play with Friends: Online/WiFi/Bluetooth
- Quick Match: 24 hours instant multiplayer
- 3D ships: collect your fleet of battleships
- Play the game in standard or classic mode
- Medals: earn medals as you rise through the ranks
- Free chat (with parental control): chat with the whole world
